                <td bgcolor="#0A0634" valign="top"><font color="#FFFFFF" face="arial" size="2"><small>Posted&nbsp;-&nbsp;04/02/2003&nbsp;: 12:46:56 PM</small><hr size="2"><span class="spnMessageText"> I'm a n00b in necromancy.  So I don't have answer but I'd like to see some.  Can someone include something about pet, dual wielding, and weapons?  what level can attack magical creature?  what level can dual wield?  does the weapon type (slash, blunt, pierce) matter?  does it matter if the weapon is non-magical?</span></font></td>
