)<br />1: Increase AC by 32 <br />2: Increase Max Hitpoints by 618 <br />3: Increase HP when cast by 618 <br />4: Increase Mana by 8 per tick<br />or<br />Protection of the Cabbage - 59 (Protection of the Glades - 60)<br />1: Increase AC by 24 <br />2: Increase Max Hitpoints by 467 (L59) to 485 (L65) <br />3: Increase HP when cast by 467 (L59) to 485 (L65) <br />4: Increase Mana by 6 per tick <br /><br />Replenishment - 61 (Blessing of Replenishment - 63)<br />1: Increase Hitpoints by 25 per tick<br /><br />SHAMAN<br />Endurance of the Boar - 62 (Talisman of the Boar - 63)<br />1: Increase STA by 60<br /><br />Focus of Soul - 62 (Focus of the Seventh 65)<br />1: Increase Max Hitpoints by 544 <br />2: Increase HP when cast by 544 <br />4: Increase STR by 75 <br />5: Increase DEX by 70 <br />6: Stacking2 v2 201: STR(75) <br />7: Stacking2 v2 201: DEX(70) <br />8: Stacking1 v2 201: STR(1075) <br />9: Stacking1 v2 201: DEX(1070) <br /><br />RANGER<br />Force of Nature - 49<br />2: Increase Damage Shield by 3 <br />3: Increase ATK by 15 <br />12: Increase Hitpoints by 3 per tick <br /><br />SELF<br />Seduction of Saryrn - 64<br />1: Illusion: Skeleton <br />2: Increase Mana by 50 per tick <br />3: Decrease Hitpoints by 63 per tick <br />4: Ultravision <br />or<br />Arch Lich - 60<br />1: Illusion: Spectre <br />2: Increase Mana by 35 per tick <br />3: Decrease Hitpoints by 53 per tick<br />4: Ultravision <br />5: See Invisible(1)<br /><br />Force Shield - 63<br />1: Increase Absorb Damage by 750 <br />2: Stacking1 v2 205: Mana(20) <br />6: Increase Mana by 2 per tick <br />or<br />Manaskin - 52<br />1: Increase Absorb Damage by 521 (L52) to 591 (L59) <br />2: Stacking1 v2 205: Mana(20) <br />6: Increase Mana by 1 per tick <br /><br />Total Effects (Best possible)<br />1: Increase Hitpoints by 57 per tick <br />2: Increase Mana by 92 per tick <br />3: Decrease Stamina Loss by 20 <br />4: Increase HP when cast by 2402 <br />5: Increase Spell Haste by 10% <br />6: Increase 