-----------<br /><br />Chanter:<br /><br />1. Gift of Brilliance (60) Mana 150, FT 2<br /><br />2. Bedlam (58) 350 Shield<br />or Uproar (63) 425 Shield<br /><br />### is probably very situational, e.g. lifeburn ###<br /><br />3. Rune V (52) 700 Shield<br />or Rune of Zebuxoruk (61) 850 Shield<br /><br />### does not stack with NECs Forceshield ###<br />-------------------------------------------<br /><br />Druid:<br /><br />1. Natureskin (57) HP 400, Regen 4<br /><br />### dont stack with resolution line and PotC and Aego/Virtue ###<br /><br />2. Protection of the Cabbage (57) HP 470, FT 6<br />or Protection of Nine (63) HP 618, FT 8<br /><br />### doesnt stack with clerics aego / virtue  and resolution line and Natreskin ###<br /><br />3. Regrowth (54) Regen 15<br />or Replenishment (61) Regen 25<br />--------------------------------------------<br /><br />Cleric:<br /><br />1. Heroism (52) 400 HP<br /><br />### doesnt stack with druids PotC and nature line and clers aego/virtue  ####<br /><br />2. Symbol of Marzin (54) HP 700<br />or Symbol of Kazad (61) HP 910<br /><br />### doesnt stack with aego / virtue ###<br /><br />3. Aegolism (60) HP 1100<br />or Virtue (62) HP 1500<br /><br />### doesnt stack with druids PotC and Nature Line and other cler HP buffs ###<br />--------------------------------------------<br /><br />Beastlord:<br /><br />1. Stamina (57) STA 40<br /><br />### same line as shams Talisman of Brute / Boar<br /><br />2. Infusion of Spirit (61) STA 55 <br /><br />### doesnt stack with shams focus ###<br /><br />3. Ferocity (65) 40 STA<br /><br />### i dont count this spell, short duration of 6 min and costs a peridot ###<br /><br />4. Talisman of Altuna (58) HP 250<br />or Talisman of Kragg (62) HP 380)<br /><br />### doesnt stack with NECs self buff and shams focus ###<br /><br />4. Spiritual Strength (60) HP 150<br />or Spiritual Vigor (62) HP 225<br /><br />### doesnt stack with Pallies Brells and Strength of Tunare and Divine Strength ###<br /><br />5. Spiritual Purity (59) Regen 7, FT 7<br />or Spiritual Dominion (64) Regen 9, FT 9<br /><br />6. Regrowth (64) Regen 15<br />---------------------------------------------<br /><br />Bard:<br /><br />1. Chorus of Replenishment (58) Regen 12, FT 13<br />or Chorus of Marr (64) Regen 20, FT 21<br /><br />### base stats, with instruments and AA a good bard should easily double ###<br />---------------------------------------------<br /><br />Necromancer (self buffs)<br /><br />1. Shield of Arcane (62) HP 300<br />or Shield of Maelin (64) HP 350<br /><br />### doesnt stack with shamans focus and talisman of Altuna / Kragg ###<br /><br />2. Archlich (60) FT 35<br />or Seduction of Saryn (64) FT 50<br /><br />### doesnt stack with chanters KEI ###<br /><br />3. Forceshield (63) Shield 750, FT 2<br /><br />### doesnt stack with Rune V and Strength of Tunare ###<br />----------------------------------------------<br /><br />so what does that mean for a NECs best raid buffs?<br /><br />1. SHM Endurance of Boar (62) STA 60<br />2. SHM Focus of Souls (62) HP 544<br />3. SHM/DRU Replenishment (61) Regen 25<br />4. PAL Brells Stalwart (65) HP 330<br />5. ENC Gift of Brilliance (60) Mana 150, FT 2<br />6. DRU Protection of Nine (63) HP 618, FT 8<br />7. CLR Symbol of Kazad (61) HP 910<br />8. BRD Chorus of Marr (64) Regen 20, FT 21<br />9. BST Spiritual Dominion (64) Regen 9, FT 9<br />10. NEC Seduction of Saryn (64) FT 50<br />11. NEC Forceshield (63) Shield 750, FT 2<br />12. RNG Force of Nature (49) Regen 3<br /><br />this adds up to HP 2402, STA 60 (around 150 HP), Regen > 57, FT > 92, Mana 150<br /><br />for me as a 63 nec with around 2100 HP unbuffed (including HP/STA food) this adds up to around 4650 HP with some insane regen and Ft (even without the 64 lich))<br /><br />Usul, Warlock 63<br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />HEY SONY, EEs are just History, like not showing DOT DMG. in your new UI, you can do it. Just SHOW IT. its all HISTORY, dot dmg and EE.<br /><br /><img src="http://frank-neugebauer.bei.t-online.de/quest.jpg" border="0"><br /><br /><br /></span></font></td>
